      <th>Sample Bit Depth</th>
      <td>24-bit</td>
    </tr>
   <tr>
       <th>Sample Rate</th>
       <td>48kHz</td>
     </tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h5 id="jpeg-2000-qualification">JPEG 2000 Qualification</h5>

<p>For providers wishing to deliver JPEG 2000 MXF OP1a masters, an on-boarding output qualification process is required before any content can be delivered. Please contact <strong>Redacted</strong> to initiate the qualification process.</p>

